init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I turn around to the people behind me, but they all seem to look like my past reincarnations.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I was driving home after my birthday party, and a drunken driver crashed into my car.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Suddenly, I begin watching a movie on the big screen in front of me.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I soon realize that this movie is about to start my new life.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The life on the big screen in front of me is similar to my previous life, but with subtle differences.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I remember that I used to take my children to a petting zoo when they were small.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I always loved looking at them experience new things.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I am no longer worried about my loved ones, because I know that they will be fine.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I feel a little bit at peace with myself, knowing that they will be taken care of.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: When I was watching this movie, I noticed that the life of my reincarnated self seemed to be an improvement from my past life.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This person was living a life that I would have wanted to live, and it seems as though everything is going well.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I am no longer upset about my death, because I know that my reincarnated self is living a much better life.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I walk outside, and I am shocked to see that the cinema which I was previously in was no longer there.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The streets were clean and people were smiling and waving at me.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: We walked for what seemed to be an hour in the wonderful city.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I walk up to the creator and I am both in awe and surprised.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She continues to tell me that I can choose to continue my life, or I can choose to go back and restart my life again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I tell the creator that I would like to continue my life, because I felt as though I could make a difference in this world.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I know that I have chosen the right life, and it will be a pleasure to live it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I never had a problem with blood and I was always interested in medicine.
